{
  "stem": "2170.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had young woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had his wife, and he had others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what he mentioned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was already '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Red Army already attacking Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Germans came in, some Romanians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we knew already news-- from Romania, came in news because they had contact from Romanian Jews came from Bucharest, whatever how they came.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were also ghettos around in that part of the Romanian Transnistria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tolochin ?] was a very big concentration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mogilev was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the [NON-ENGLISH] and the [NON-ENGLISH]-- no, the [NON-ENGLISH] Between Romania, Bessarabia, and the Ukraine, there were a big concentration of Jews in ghetto, mostly Romanian Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many, many were killed in the beginning, but not regular liquidated in graves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But killed wherever they run, wherever they didn't work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were Hungarian Jews coming in with certain Stars of David.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were doctors with the Hungarian Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were also savages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somehow, they said they were going on the front line towards Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Meantime, Zhmerinka was a very big center of German concentration.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Trains all over Russia because it was between-- going out from Russia towards Western Europe, Poland, and Romania, and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I could see all the Germans running here and there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As soon as Stalingrad fell, the Germans start to run in a certain way back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was already 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was going to work-- slave workery-- working--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All kind.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took me-- actually, the Jewish police in the ghetto took me to work to load trains-- Romanian trains, German trains-- because I had mentioned-- was a big railroad center.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So trains with the coal, trains with all kinds of things-- you had to put it in a wagon full of coal.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
